Description:
Delivers an attack with a potency of 3,000.

※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
Delivers an attack with a potency of 3,000. Combo Action: Barbarous Bite ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 4,000. Combo Action: Steel Fangs Additional Effect: Grants Hunter's Instinct Hunter's Instinct Effect: Increases damage dealt by 10% Duration: 15s Extends Hunter's Instinct duration by 15s to a maximum of 30s. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 4,000. Combo Action: Piercing Fangs Additional Effect: Grants Swiftscaled Swiftscaled Effect: Reduces weaponskill recast time by 20% Duration: 15s Extends Swiftscaled duration by 15s to a maximum of 30s. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
Delivers an attack with a potency of 5,000. Combo Action: Hunter's Sting ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
対象に物理攻撃。　威力：5000 ●単体二刀流WS：3B強化効果中威力：7000 コンボ条件：●単体二刀流WS：2A 追加効果：自身に「●単体合体剣アビリティ実行可」を付与する。 効果時間：15秒 発動条件：「●単体二刀流WS：3B強化」効果中 ※このアクションはホットバーに登録することはできない。
Delivers an attack with a potency of 5,000. Combo Action: Swiftskin's Sting ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
対象に物理攻撃。　威力：5000 ●単体二刀流WS：3D強化効果中威力：8000 コンボ条件：●単体二刀流WS：2B 追加効果：自身に「●単体合体剣アビリティ実行可」を付与する。 効果時間：15秒 発動条件：「●単体二刀流WS：3D強化」効果中 ※このアクションはホットバーに登録することはできない。
対象に物理攻撃。　威力：8000 このウェポンスキルは固有のリキャストタイマーを持つ。 最大チャージ数：2

Delivers an attack with a potency of 8,000. Additional Effect: Grants Hunter's Instinct Hunter's Instinct Effect: Increases damage dealt by 10% Duration: 15s Extends Hunter's Instinct duration by 15s to a maximum of 30s. Maximum Charges: 2 This weaponskill does not share a recast timer with any other actions. ※Action changes to Swiftskin's Coil upon execution.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 8,000. Combo Action: Hunter's Snap Additional Effect: Grants Swiftscaled Swiftscaled Effect: Reduces weaponskill recast time by 20% Duration: 15s Extends Swiftscaled duration by 15s to a maximum of 30s. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 8,000 to target and all enemies nearby it.
Potency is increased by 50% when attacking only a single target.
This weaponskill does not share a recast timer with any other actions.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 5,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Combo Action: World-swallower Can only be executed while under the effect of Reawakened. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 5,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Combo Action: First Generation Can only be executed while under the effect of Reawakened. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 5,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Combo Action: Second Generation Can only be executed while under the effect of Reawakened. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 5,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Combo Action: Third Generation Can only be executed while under the effect of Reawakened. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 10,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Additional Effect: Extends Hunter's Instinct and Swiftscaled duration by 15s to a maximum of 30s Can only be executed while under the effect of Reawakened. Effect fades upon execution. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 3,000. Ignores the effects of Guard when dealing damage. Additional Effect: Adds 3 seconds of charge to the limit gauge Can only be executed after successfully landing Barbarous Bite or Ravenous Bite. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 3,000. Ignores the effects of Guard when dealing damage. Additional Effect: Adds 3 seconds of charge to the limit gauge Can only be executed after successfully landing Hunter's Snap. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 3,000. Ignores the effects of Guard when dealing damage. Additional Effect: Adds 3 seconds of charge to the limit gauge Can only be executed after successfully landing Swiftskin's Coil. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 3,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Ignores the effects of Guard when dealing damage. Additional Effect: Adds 3 seconds of charge to the limit gauge Can only be executed after successfully landing Uncoiled Fury. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
対象とその周囲の敵に物理攻撃。　威力：2000 追加効果：自身のリミットゲージを増加させる。 効果時間：10秒 発動条件：「●遠隔二刀流アビリティ：B実行可」効果中 ※このアクションはホットバーに登録することはできない。

Delivers an attack with a potency of 3,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Ignores the effects of Guard when dealing damage. Additional Effect: Adds 3 seconds of charge to the limit gauge Can only be executed after successfully landing First Generation. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 3,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Ignores the effects of Guard when dealing damage. Additional Effect: Adds 3 seconds of charge to the limit gauge Can only be executed after successfully landing Second Generation. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 3,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Ignores the effects of Guard when dealing damage. Additional Effect: Adds 3 seconds of charge to the limit gauge Can only be executed after successfully landing Third Generation. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 3,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Ignores the effects of Guard when dealing damage. Additional Effect: Adds 3 seconds of charge to the limit gauge Can only be executed after successfully landing Fourth Generation. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
Changes to Death Rattle, Twinfang Bite, Twinblood Bite, Uncoiled Twinfang, First Legacy, Second Legacy, Third Legacy, or Fourth Legacy when requirements for execution are met.

Rush to a targeted enemy's or party member's location. Additional Effect: Grants Slither Slither Effect: Increases damage dealt by next weaponskill by 25% Duration: 10s Maximum Charges: 3 Unable to cast if bound.

Grants Hardened Scales, changing Snake Scales to Backlash. Hardened Scales Effect: Reduces damage taken by 50% and grants immunity to Stun, Heavy, Bind, Silence, Half-asleep, Sleep, Deep Freeze, and knockback and draw-in effects Duration: 4s Additional Effect: Grants Armored Scales to self, creating a barrier that nullifies damage equivalent to a heal of 6,000 potency Duration: 4s Grants Snake's Bane when barrier is completely absorbed. Waiting 4s or executing Backlash while under the effect of Hardened Scales delivers an attack with a potency of 6,000 to all enemies within 5 yalms. Range is increased by 15 yalms and potency is doubled for enemies within 5 yalms while under the effect of Snake's Bane. Unable to move while under the effect of Hardened Scales.

Delivers an attack with a potency of 6,000 to all nearby enemies. Additional Effect: Absorbs 50% of damage dealt as HP Range is increased by 15 yalms and potency is doubled for enemies within 5 yalms while under the effect of Snake's Bane. Hardened Scales and Snake's Bane effects expire upon execution. Can only be executed while under the effect of Hardened Scales. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
Resets the recast timer for Uncoiled Fury and Snake Scales. Recast time is reduced by 10s upon earning a kill or an assist.

Delivers a jumping physical attack to target and all enemies nearby it with a potency of 10,000. Additional Effect: Grants Reawakened Duration: 20s Additional Effect: Afflicts target with Noxious Gnash Noxious Gnash Effect: Increases damage you deal target by 20% Duration: 10s Additional Effect: Heavy +75% Duration: 5s Can only be executed when the limit gauge is full. Gauge Charge Time: 90s ※Dual Fang Combo changes to First Generation while under the effect of Reawakened. ※Hunter's Snap changes to Ouroboros while under the effect of Reawakened.

Delivers fire damage with a potency of 3,000. Additional Effect: Grants Aetherhues Duration: 15s Cannot be cast while under the effect of Subtractive Palette. ※Fire in Red changes to Aero in Green while under the effect of Aetherhues. ※Fire in Red changes to Water in Blue while under the effect of Aetherhues II. ※Fire in Red changes to Blizzard in Cyan while under the effect of Subtractive Palette. ※Fire in Red changes to Stone in Yellow while under the effect of Subtractive Palette and Aetherhues. ※Fire in Red changes to Thunder in Magenta while under the effect of Subtractive Palette and Aetherhues II.
Delivers wind damage with a potency of 4,000. Additional Effect: Grants Aetherhues II Duration: 15s Can only be cast while under the effect of Aetherhues. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
Delivers water damage with a potency of 5,000. Can only be cast while under the effect of Aetherhues II. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers ice damage with a potency of 6,000. Additional Effect: Grants Aetherhues Duration: 15s Can only be cast while under the effect of Subtractive Palette. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Delivers earth damage with a potency of 7,000. Additional Effect: Grants Aetherhues II Duration: 15s Can only be cast while under the effect of Subtractive Palette and Aetherhues. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
Delivers lightning damage with a potency of 8,000. Can only be cast while under the effect of Subtractive Palette and Aetherhues II. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
対象に向かって前方直線範囲魔法攻撃。　威力：16000 発動条件：「●虹色のインク」効果中

Deals unaspected damage with a potency of 8,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Additional Effect: Restores own HP Cure Potency: 8,000 Maximum Charges: 2 Cannot be cast while under the effect of Subtractive Palette. Shares a recast timer with Comet in Black. ※Holy in White changes to Comet in Black while under the effect of Subtractive Palette.

Deals unaspected damage with a potency of 12,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Maximum Charges: 2 Can only be cast while under the effect Subtractive Palette. Shares a recast timer with Holy in White. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Paints a pom, granting Pom Motif. Can only be cast while under the effect of Pom Sketch. The recast timer of this action is not affected by status effects. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Paints a pair of wings, granting Wing Motif. Can only be cast while under the effect of Wing Sketch. The recast timer of this action is not affected by status effects. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Paints a claw, granting Claw Motif. Can only be cast while under the effect of Claw Sketch. The recast timer of this action is not affected by status effects. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Paints a maw, granting Maw Motif. Can only be cast while under the effect of Maw Sketch. The recast timer of this action is not affected by status effects. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Paints a creature motif. This action changes to Pom Motif, Wing Motif, Claw Motif, or Maw Motif based on your current creature sketch. The recast timer of this action is not affected by status effects.

Render a rain of poms, dealing unaspected damage with a potency of 4,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Additional Effect: Increases damage dealt and healing potency by 20% Duration: 10s Additional Effect: Grants Wing Sketch Maximum Charges: 2 Can only be cast while under the effect of Pom Motif. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Render a pair of windborne wings, dealing unaspected damage with a potency of 6,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Additional Effect: Reduces spell cast time and recast time by 20%, while also increasing movement speed by 25% Duration: 10s Additional Effect: Grants Moogle Portrait Additional Effect: Grants Claw Sketch Maximum Charges: 2 Can only be cast while under the effect of Wing Motif. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Render a sharpened claw, dealing unaspected damage with a potency of 4,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Additional Effect: Increases target's damage taken by 10%, while reducing HP recovered by healing actions by 20% Duration: 10s Additional Effect: Grants Maw Sketch Maximum Charges: 2 Can only be cast while under the effect of Claw Motif. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Render a set of ferocious fangs, dealing unaspected damage with a potency of 8,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Additional Effect: Damage over time Potency: 4,000 Duration: 12s Additional Effect: Grants Madeen Portrait Additional Effect: Grants Pom Sketch Maximum Charges: 2 Can only be cast while under the effect of Maw Motif. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.

Render your depiction of a creature to life. This action changes to Pom Muse, Winged Muse, Clawed Muse, or Fanged Muse based on your current motif. The recast timer of this action is not affected by status effects.
Quickly dash 15 yalms forward. Additional Effect: Increases movement speed Duration: 5s Cannot be executed while bound.

Grants Tempera Coat. Tempera Coat Effect: Erects a magicked barrier which nullifies damage equivalent to a heal of 12,000 potency Duration: 10s Reduces the recast time of Tempera Coat by 10 seconds when barrier is completely absorbed. ※Tempera Coat changes to Tempera Grassa while under the effect of Tempera Coat.

Ends the effect of Tempera Coat and grants Tempera Grassa to self and nearby party members. Tempera Grassa Effect: Erects a magicked barrier which nullifies damage equivalent to a heal of 6,000 potency Duration: 10s Reduces the recast time of Tempera Coat by 5 seconds when barrier is completely absorbed. Can only be executed while under the effect of Tempera Coat. ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
Grants Subtractive Palette. Effect ends upon reuse.
Cancels the effect of Subtractive Palette.

Render a fat chocobo, knocking back all enemies within range 10 yalms. Additional Effect: Creates a Chocobastion at your feet, reducing damage taken by 25% while increasing HP recovered by healing actions by 25% for self and all party members within the area Duration: 15s Additional Effect: Grants Starstruck Duration: 15s Can only be executed when the limit gauge is full. Gauge Charge Time: 105s ※Advent of Chocobastion changes to Star Prism while Chocobastion is active.

Deals unaspected damage with a potency of 12,000 to target and all enemies nearby it. Additional Effect: Restores HP of all party members within 30 yalms of target, and grants healing over time Cure Potency: 8,000 Heal Over Time Potency: 2,000 Duration: 12s ※This action cannot be assigned to a hotbar.
